analyze_sleep_results.promptTemplate:
Analyze these sleep cycle results and suggest improvements.

Consolidation: {consolidation}
Error analysis: {errorAnalysis}
Memory pruning: {pruning}

Identify patterns, inefficiencies, and actionable improvements.

Respond with JSON only: {"insights": ["insight text", ...], "suggestions": [{"observation": "what was observed", "suggestion": "what to do", "priority": "high" or "medium" or "low"}]}

generate_reflection.promptTemplate:
Reflect on these sleep cycle metrics and generate insights about system behavior.

Sleep results summary: {summary}

Analyze learning effectiveness, error patterns, memory health, and suggest adjustments.

Respond with JSON only: {"insights": ["insight text", ...], "adjustments": [{"type": "category", "suggestion": "what to adjust"}]}
